{"tid":728375,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【揭當年夾定打曾江】四哥爆：嗰時係做戲嘅！","createTime":"2018-07-03T17:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T16:03:42.000Z","uid":150685,"like":40,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a3547cff5a9ff78fd4db439aad12bfa8489a8f80","tid":728375,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180703/large/1530631521_46c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180703%2Flarge%2F1530631521_46c4.jpg&h=b90c1a5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四哥謝賢今晚喺尖沙嘴出席鮑魚宴，同前妻狄波拉、鬍鬚Kong同胡楓（修哥）同場，四哥精神奕奕、談笑風生，佢提到自己回復單身，好彩跟個仔霆鋒去拍《鋒味》搵番兩個錢自己使，問四哥會唔會有旅遊節目搵佢做？佢就話：「有人請我做乜都做！唔知係咪覺得我老，我好有魄力㗎！」<br />\n<br />\n問到四哥o依家係咪嚴選對手、唔再《4個小生去旅行》時有積怨而動手嘅曾江合作？四哥即大爆內幕話：「痴線嘅！我哋o依家唔知幾friend，嗰時係做戲嘅！」<br />\n咪住！回一回帶先，事緣2015年四哥、修哥、曾江同Joe Junior一齊宣傳大台節目《4個小生去旅行》，喺記招上四哥疑與曾江有積怨，突然喺記招上出手摑曾江，修哥勸交時被打飛眼鏡，場面混亂（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IQgDZp）。o依家四哥咁講，咁即係&hellip;&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IQgDZp%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82o%E4%BE%9D%E5%AE%B6%E5%9B%9B%E5%93%A5%E5%92%81%E8%AC%9B%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%81%E5%8D%B3%E4%BF%82%E2%80%A6%E2%80%A6&d=YGuXdyIPxNHJymgc9B69yZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=868d27bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IQgDZp）。o依家四哥咁講，咁即係&hellip;&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n記者笑問佢哋真好戲，四哥續說：「真到不得了！」修哥連眼鏡都飛埋出嚟喎？四哥話：「佢自己做㗎嘛，佢用手指撳住個眼鏡，佢好好戲，係老戲骨，好戲過我哋好多。嗰巴係四個人一齊度邊個做，係擺我上枱，我個人有乜所謂啫，咁一巴，我幾威呀，不知幾過癮！但係後尾就唔過癮呀，因為個個指住我鬧，幾陰功呀，做埋啲咁嘅衰嘢！」<br />\n<br />\n問四哥有冇請曾江食飯賠罪？佢話：「打完之後即刻請佢食雪糕啦，等佢冷番。o依家先爆都未遲，真係㗎！做電影出盡辦法宣傳，幾衰呀！係我謝老四先咁蠢。佢哋本身係搵胡楓做嘅，但係佢講嘢啊啊啊&hellip;咁樣鬼聽佢呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180703/58396517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F58396517&d=YGuXdyIPxNHJymgc9B69yZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=a316c326\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F58396517&h=97bfbddf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180703/58396517</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三個老鬼做場大龍凰"},{"pid":"3b307ad3950ce524f85b33a460155a627b863ba9","tid":728375,"uid":24160,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"冇人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7597987d38776b07423040f7827d01d71e15d3","tid":728375,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ca38575da1882de2353cce280e74ed299ea142","tid":728375,"uid":56758,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"睇黎無線就快拍多輯<br />\n謝老四開始出黎鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c271b3655d7db2470eba22052c69b499f0590e1","tid":728375,"uid":158270,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b307ad3950ce524f85b33a460155a627b863ba9","tid":728375,"uid":24160,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"冇人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:44:58.000Z","msg":"Why are you here"},{"pid":"13b9e3e9d2a74ec1d889995ac04f0815c360ae75","tid":728375,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾到而家都仲未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ea2cf27182676545afed90a39a28f50d1cefe2","tid":728375,"uid":58247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":